==== 菲律宾华人 ====
{{main|菲律宾华人}}
菲律賓華人，几乎遍佈全菲各地。據統計，目前在[[菲律賓人口|菲律賓人口]]的華人約有百萬，其中先祖來自[[福建|福建]][[閩南|閩南]]者（[[泉州|泉州]]、[[漳州|漳州]]、[[廈門|廈門]]）十之八九，當中又以泉州為最，其餘約百分之十，以[[广东省|廣東]]籍為多。

福建籍華人中，以原屬[[泉州府|泉州府]]的[[泉州三邑|三邑]]（[[晉江縣|晉江縣]]、[[惠安縣|惠安縣]]、[[南安縣|南安縣]]）等縣最多，大部份居住在[[呂宋|呂宋島]]，尤其是大馬尼拉地區，所經營的工商業和文教事業，也以在大馬尼拉地區的最為發達<ref name="7 mother tounges">[http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/317280/news/nation/deped-adds-7-languages-to-mother-tongue-based-education-for-kinder-to-grade-3 DepEd adds 7 languages to mother tongue-based education for Kinder to Grade 3] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/317280/news/nation/deped-adds-7-languages-to-mother-tongue-based-education-for-kinder-to-grade-3 |date=20170221210849 }}. GMA News. 7/13/2013.</ref><ref name="7 mother tounges">[http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/317280/news/nation/deped-adds-7-languages-to-mother-tongue-based-education-for-kinder-to-grade-3 DepEd adds 7 languages to mother tongue-based education for Kinder to Grade 3] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/317280/news/nation/deped-adds-7-languages-to-mother-tongue-based-education-for-kinder-to-grade-3 |date=20170221210849 }}. GMA News. 7/13/2013.</ref>。

原屬[[泉州府|泉州府]][[同安縣|同安縣]]（今[[廈門市|廈門市]]和[[金門縣|金門縣]]）、[[漳州府|漳州府]][[龙溪县|龍溪]]、[[海澄县|海澄]]（今合併為[[龙海市|龍海市]]）等，大多數在中部[[維薩亞斯|維薩亞斯]]地區的[[宿霧島|宿霧]]等地，和[[民答那峨島|民答那峨島]]各處<ref name="#1">{{cite web|url=http://www.ethnologue.com/country/ph/languages/|title=Philippines|publisher=[[Ethnologue|Ethnologue]]|accessdate=2019-04-05|archive-date=2019-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430170623/https://www.ethnologue.com/country/ph/languages|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="7 mother tounges">[http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/317280/news/nation/deped-adds-7-languages-to-mother-tongue-based-education-for-kinder-to-grade-3 DepEd adds 7 languages to mother tongue-based education for Kinder to Grade 3] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gmanetwork.com/news/story/317280/news/nation/deped-adds-7-languages-to-mother-tongue-based-education-for-kinder-to-grade-3 |date=20170221210849 }}. GMA News. 7/13/2013.</ref>。

